About me

Juan J. Quiroz O.

I'm a robotics researcher at The University of Tokyo.

Research Interests

My research interests focus on modeling and control of constrained redundant robots, as mobile manipulators, humanoid robots and surgical robots.

Current Research

Currently, I am working on constrained control strategies for surgical robots exploiting the robot dynamics.
